English: Emergency power supply unit: <color=orange>ONLINE.</color> Door to <color=orange>ZONE 186</color> unlocked.
Description: A text string that appears on screen when the player attempts to open a door which is locked due to an emergency lockdown. Don't alter the RichText tags.

Italian.Translation: Alimentatore di emergenza: <color=orange>ONLINE.</color> Porta per <color=orange>ZONE 186</color> sbloccata.

Spanish.Translation: Unidad eléctrica de apoyo: <color=orange>ACTIVADA.</color> La puerta a la <color=orange>ZONE 186</color> se ha desbloqueado.

Russian.Translation: Аварийный источник питания: <color=orange>ВКЛЮЧЕН</color>. Дверь в <color=orange>ZONE 186</color> разблокирована.

Portuguese_Brazil.Translation: Unidade de fornecimento elétrico de emergência: <color=orange>ONLINE</color> Porta para a <color=orange>ZONE 186</color> destravada.

Polish.Translation: Awaryjna jednostka zasilająca: <color=orange>WŁĄCZONA.</color> Drzwi do <color=orange>strefy 186 [ZONE_186]</color> odblokowane.
